Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好梅萨  伤势怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始回归任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止已经被梅萨救了好多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这样  真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后  停止银河苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是风之王国苹果  以及遗迹内水的军方供给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查之前的供货商之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了不符合实情的伪装公司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据战术调查  更进一步发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fn微软雅黑\bord3\pos(511.8,660)}Seiðgalður\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\bord3}　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　Fold\N{\fs45\bord1\blur0}水和苹果合成的「引导者」  能够促成「折跃细菌」的增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而促进狂暴化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的狂暴症
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}　　　　  　　　　　　　Fold\N{\fs45}就是寄生在细胞内的「折跃细菌」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将强烈的感情通过亚空间传播  放大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人类狂暴化的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  我们女武神的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从拥有能够抑制这种细菌的影响的特别因子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Fold Receptor　　　　　\N{\fs45}也就是「折跃受体」的人群中选出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是通过这种因子的力量抑制狂暴化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神选拔也就是为了寻找  接收因子的拥有者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾风·因梅尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那个拥有者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  疾风也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  准备等有机会了跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在博尔德的战斗中  疾风的接收因子数值突然迅速增长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是和芙蕾雅产生共鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和  疾风…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  拥有接收因子的人不容易狂暴化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有接收因子的我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要认真听我的歌声  就没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  已经一度狂暴化的人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有根本的治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可能受到风之王国的风之歌声的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前  因为狂暴者全灭的的行星\N「阿尔夫海姆」的都市「马利安布鲁克」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说中尉就是那里的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重伤之际被阿拉德队长救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  那个时候就已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  我去跟队长说也可以啊  关于你之前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  我曾经一度狂暴化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事队长也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长也知道？  那个鱿鱼干大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次发病的事情队长也知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么办  只是继续执行任务罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到才怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话结束了  回基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了  继续说也没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…  要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情就别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨中尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蜇祭典  今年也是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  阿疾和小米拉在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳下两个人都不说话气氛好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裸喰娘娘疾风的房间里也好像有好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房…房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽安的情报不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐妻关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐妻…关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才8点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AXIA那首歌  是要小姐唱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美云来之前  我还是王牌时候的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  其实在进入女武神之前就作为偶像出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直没红起来  一度隐退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  也没放弃梦想东奔西走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Fold Receptor     　　　　　　　　　\N{\fs45}托了折跃受体的福  加入了女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是我作为女武神的王牌最后的一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  女武神的王牌是美云
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有作为王牌的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  自己说有点那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像作为队长比较适合引导大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿格帕特拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个星球也拥有的  普洛特文明遗迹中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能确认  它是否会对我们的歌声产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在博尔德是有反应的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被占领的星球中  有多个普洛特文明遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然每个都  正对所在行星的中央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Energy Shift     　 　　　　\N{\fs45}「能量迁移」也在增长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别提和歌声的关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连它们的功能是什么  到现在也无法阐明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨  你没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨·伊雷菲尔特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻重返任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没击中吗  明明都三对一了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个模拟战  难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  梅萨他正把我们当作白骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他还想和白骑士决斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 3 4 5被击坠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危机正在逼近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗从这里才进入正题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解队内的战力  身为指挥官是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐妻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾风和米拉洁小姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  梅萨为什么要如此执著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有中尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也担心自己的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}　　　　  Fold Receptor\N{\fs45}我没有折跃受体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一哪天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有芙蕾雅在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有她的歌声在就不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有芙蕾雅小姐的  有女武神的歌在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果和水  凭已经运出去的量就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹的事  不是也已经被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有风之歌者的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查  我们已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧  并不需要风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时感受到的  那阵风是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璐姆好慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和队长商量下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算继续当飞行员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没和白骑士分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道说  只凭我们打倒不了他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉你有可能会被敌人控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  就把我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经明确说过  要把敌人击坠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的意思是  在变成那样之前先去别处避一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和要小姐之间有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  在说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只手镯里仅有一首要小姐的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歌声拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让失去理智的我清醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保护救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空袭警报？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急召集…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空系统内侧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}　　　　　Fold\N{\fs45}疑似出现脱离折跃的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前未发生狂暴症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Hemera              　\N{\fs45}偏偏在「赫墨拉」不在的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧  女武神和delta小队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中骑士团  参上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做过头了哦  波克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta小队  准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复  Delta小队  准备起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞧我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta小队  起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没听到风之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这待机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然冲上别人的舞台  胆子真大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中  集中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦  Delta 5
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现你了  地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我用你们的血把这片天染红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 5  我去掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  米拉洁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起来了  打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  遗迹在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7点上方  有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 5  右侧攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨  怎么了梅萨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长  提前出动女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快一点  梅萨要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨君出了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧  女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨中尉  梅萨中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨中尉  听得到吗  梅萨中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta 2  请回答  梅萨中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖被打下去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都可倾听风声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的援军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是紧追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机返回树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久违了啊  能看到璐姆出现如此色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您早就知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件是定期发送数据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M女士已经和我跟阿拉德谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这样太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾风和米拉洁小姐  救了梅萨先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我这边不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去吹会儿风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅…梅萨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得自己太难为情了  受不了了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说风之王国的人只能活到三十岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会觉得不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下的生活被挤得满满的  根本没时间去想以后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被挤得满满的生活吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准这样也蛮好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
